  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play! Die! Repeat!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/23d23b0c4cbd128e59024dd61ae3486e.poster.avif?t=1648078578\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/23d23b0c4cbd128e59024dd61ae3486e.webm?t=1648078578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/23d23b0c4cbd128e59024dd61ae3486e.mp4?t=1648078578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rejoinder is an endless, repeatable roguelite game with procedural generated levels where you must defeat the army of skeletons, evil warriors, and powerful bosses. Collect coins to upgrade your sword, and buy stronger potions for your character.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/b489914f6a7912b18566bb38caf78f6e.poster.avif?t=1648078578\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/b489914f6a7912b18566bb38caf78f6e.webm?t=1648078578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824070/extras/b489914f6a7912b18566bb38caf78f6e.mp4?t=1648078578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Destroy your enemies!<br></li><li>Defeat powerful bosses!<br></li><li>Level up, and collet new weapons and magics!<br></li><li>Buy stat potions such as Strength, Speed, Health, Stamina, and more!<br></li><li>Play, die, and repeat!. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Generated Levels! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsi